sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant EPP as EPP (Endpoint Picker)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DecodeSidecar as P/D Decode Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
    participant PrefillWorker as Prefill Worker Pod<br/>varies/TCP
    participant LocalVLLM as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP
    participant ZMQ as vLLM KV Events<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ

    Note over Client,LocalVLLM: Flow 1: Standard Inference Request (Non-P/D)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc request<br/>gRPC/9002 plaintext
    EPP->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool/Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>EPP: Pool & Pod state
    Note over EPP: Run filter/score pipeline:<br/>by-label → load-aware → prefix-cache
    EPP-->>Gateway: Selected pod endpoint<br/>gRPC/9002
    Gateway->>LocalVLLM: Forward to selected pod<br/>HTTP/8000
    LocalVLLM-->>Gateway: Inference response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,LocalVLLM: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/80
    Gateway->>EPP: ext-proc request<br/>gRPC/9002 plaintext
    Note over EPP: P/D profile selected:<br/>pd-profile handler
    EPP-->>Gateway: Decode pod + x-prefiller-host-port header<br/>gRPC/9002
    Gateway->>DecodeSidecar: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8000 TLS 1.2+
    Note over DecodeSidecar: SSRF validation:<br/>Check prefill target in allowlist
    DecodeSidecar->>PrefillWorker: Prefill request<br/>HTTP(S)/varies Optional TLS
    PrefillWorker-->>DecodeSidecar: Prefill result
    DecodeSidecar->>LocalVLLM: Decode request<br/>HTTP(S)/8001 Optional TLS
    LocalVLLM-->>DecodeSidecar: Decode response
    DecodeSidecar-->>Gateway: Streaming response<br/>HTTPS/8000
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response

    Note over EPP,ZMQ: Flow 3: KV Cache Event Streaming
    ZMQ->>EPP: KV cache events<br/>ZMQ SUB/5557 plaintext
    Note over EPP: Update precise-prefix-cache<br/>scorer with KV state
